@startuml sequence_diagram_kelola_pasien
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence Diagram Kelola Data Pasien\nSistem Prediksi Penyebaran DBD

actor "Petugas" as User
participant "Halaman\nData Pasien" as Page
participant "Controller\nPasien" as Controller
database "Database" as DB

== Menampilkan Daftar Pasien ==
User -> Page : Buka menu Data Pasien
activate Page

Page -> Controller : Request daftar pasien
activate Controller

Controller -> DB : SELECT * FROM pasien_dbd
activate DB
DB --> Controller : Return data pasien
deactivate DB

Controller --> Page : Kirim data pasien
Page --> User : Tampilkan tabel pasien
deactivate Controller

== Tambah Data Pasien ==
User -> Page : Klik tombol Tambah
Page --> User : Tampilkan form input

User -> Page : Input data pasien
Page -> Controller : Submit form
activate Controller

Controller -> Controller : Validasi data
Controller -> DB : INSERT INTO pasien_dbd
activate DB
DB --> Controller : Success
deactivate DB

Controller -> DB : INSERT INTO log_aktivitas
Controller --> Page : Response sukses
Page --> User : Tampilkan alert sukses

deactivate Controller

== Edit Data Pasien ==
User -> Page : Klik tombol Edit
Page -> Controller : Request data by ID
activate Controller
Controller -> DB : SELECT * WHERE id=?
activate DB
DB --> Controller : Return data
deactivate DB
Controller --> Page : Kirim data
deactivate Controller
Page --> User : Tampilkan form edit

User -> Page : Update data
Page -> Controller : Submit update
activate Controller
Controller -> DB : UPDATE pasien_dbd
activate DB
DB --> Controller : Success
deactivate DB
Controller --> Page : Response sukses
Page --> User : Tampilkan alert sukses
deactivate Controller

== Hapus Data Pasien ==
User -> Page : Klik tombol Hapus
Page --> User : Konfirmasi hapus

User -> Page : Konfirmasi Ya
Page -> Controller : Request delete
activate Controller
Controller -> DB : DELETE FROM pasien_dbd
activate DB
DB --> Controller : Success
deactivate DB
Controller --> Page : Response sukses
Page --> User : Refresh halaman
deactivate Controller

deactivate Page

@enduml
